{"tid":1999610,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日燒山下午茶","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T04:33:30.000Z","uid":129042,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b33d27176b2827e9c7a2969cbeaf2adcfc0e7108","tid":1999610,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U10nTVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU10nTVs.png&h=d4872e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5p4Dsfz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5p4Dsfz.png&h=c38bc660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT47 咖喱牛腩飯 $46<br />\n加埋炒蛋同牛角包 +$8<br />\n<br />\n喺連登吹左風之後<br />\n今日炮台山店好撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔左塊膠板，所以影出嚟嘅顏色怪怪地請見諒<br />\n咖喱同出邊嘅茶餐廳好唔同<br />\n應該加咗好多唔同嘅香料<br />\n不過牛腩舊舊都好唔同<br />\n應該放咗唔同嘅部位，其中有一舊咬到好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己唔係太熟牛腩，但係我估佢就係牛爽腩<br />\n炒蛋有少少似大快活嗰種炒蛋<br />\n落咗賴落去炒非常滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋牛角包今次係新鮮出爐外脆內軟<br />\n今次真係有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫咗杯熱鴛鴦，茶味好出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飲得出咖啡係即磨咖啡，唔係用粉沖個種<br />\n<br />\n8.9/10分<br />\n<br />\n我唔會學印度吧咁講食落喉嚨好舒服<br />\n淨係想講，$54蚊咁多嘢<br />\n真係連晚餐都唔使食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwfCHO0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwfCHO0.png&h=29ac724a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場加映<br />\n時代冰室推出左燉湯<br />\n燒山正式同燉宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完行過隔離楊明燉間鋪<br />\n竟然得返一個廢老喺度飲垃圾湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死"},{"pid":"a20094af1289b3dd50bbffab61106745527d6b63","tid":1999610,"uid":225996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"巴打你一日四餐都係時代冰室？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 食過唔錯"},{"pid":"fd2780e817b6b3b9372c87e2106266a5b1af5090","tid":1999610,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"燉湯加20蚊超平"},{"pid":"2ad03061524deaf199f62e73e212c2989f61c551","tid":1999610,"uid":228143,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a20094af1289b3dd50bbffab61106745527d6b63","tid":1999610,"uid":225996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"巴打你一日四餐都係時代冰室？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 食過唔錯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"好正常者<br />\n時代咁多款<br />\n輪住食<br />\n一個月都唔會重覆一次好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d21ae2b82ea36d9e77d77d28529e851eeb5ec7d","tid":1999610,"uid":129042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a20094af1289b3dd50bbffab61106745527d6b63","tid":1999610,"uid":225996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"巴打你一日四餐都係時代冰室？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 食過唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"一日一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過炮台山周邊都多黃店<br />\n有時會食其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c4ed983023b55c4b3cdd4edf872f624f3c92e1","tid":1999610,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd2780e817b6b3b9372c87e2106266a5b1af5090","tid":1999610,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"燉湯加20蚊